            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-8 w-7 h-7 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm font-bold ring-2 ring-white">3</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mb-1">Коммерческое предложение</h3>
